citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 310 pm on
25-JUL-17. Inspector found no answer at house door, waited 30 minutes, called phone number on file and left
message.
